# Placeholder so docker-compose has a valid env_file when ENV_FILE is not set.
# Replace with your real .env (or set ENV_FILE) for DATABASE_URL, etc.
# For Grafana Cloud metrics, add: GRAFANA_CLOUD_PROMETHEUS_REMOTE_WRITE_URL, GRAFANA_CLOUD_USER, GRAFANA_CLOUD_API_KEY
# For Grafana Cloud logs, add: GRAFANA_CLOUD_LOKI_URL, GRAFANA_CLOUD_LOKI_USER
# Set LOG_FORMAT=json for structured JSON logging (recommended in production)
